---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';

// These variables make it easy to update your info in one place
const title = "About Me";
const description = "Mechanical Engineering student at The Ohio State University";
const pubDate = new Date('March 30 2026');
const heroImage = '/blog-placeholder-about.jpg'; // Ensure this file exists in your public folder
---

<Layout 
	title={title} 
	description={description} 
	pubDate={pubDate} 
>
	<div class="about-content">
		<p>
			I am a pre-mechanical engineering student at <strong>The Ohio State University</strong>, 
			where I am currently tackling the rigors of Math 1172, Physics 1250, and Engr 1182. 
			Beyond the technical formulas, I am pursuing a minor in Philosoph, a personal passion 
			that drives me to understand the ethical and logical foundations of the world we build.
		</p>

		<p>
			My approach to life is defined by high-intensity discipline. Whether I am training 
			for the physical demands of the <strong>firefighter physical test</strong> or 
			executing a "hardcore" 90-day personal transformation, I believe that mastery 
			is the result of consistent, focused effort.
		</p>

		<p>
			Outside of my academic and physical training, I’m a drummer and a creator. 
			I’m currently focused on expanding my skill set into graphic design and 
			copywriting, aiming to blend technical engineering expertise with 
			effective communication.
		</p>

		<section class="current-goals">
			<h2>Current Focus</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Major:</strong> Mechanical Engineering (OSU)</li>
				<li><strong>Minor:</strong> Philosophy</li>
				<li><strong>Training:</strong> Firefighter Physical Readiness</li>
				<li><strong>Projects:</strong> Building a professional digital presence</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<div class="cta">
			<p>Want to connect or talk shop about engineering?</p>
			<a href="mailto:thelandonjgreen@gmail.com" class="contact-button">Reach Out</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-content {
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #333;
	}

	.about-content p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.current-goals {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: #f8f9fa;
		border-left: 4px solid #ba0c2f; /* OSU Scarlet */
		border-radius: 4px;
	}

	.current-goals h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: #ba0c2f;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.current-goals ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.current-goals li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.cta {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #eee;
	}

	.contact-button {
		display: inline-block;
		background: #ba0c2f;
		color: white;
		padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 5px;
